<HL>
   Telxon Buys Debentures
</HL>
<DATE>
04/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C21
</SO>
<CO>
   TLXN
</CO>
<IN>
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   AKRON, Ohio -- Telxon Corp. said it completed the purchase
of $10 million of its 7.5% convertible subordinated
debentures, due 2012.
   The purchase represents about 22% of the issue
outstanding, leaving about $36 million outstanding.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Telxon makes hand-held computers and computer systems.
</TEXT>
